---
title: Bulgogi-Style Chicken with Roasted Carrots & Lemony Rice
description: If you can’t get enough of Korean-inspired flavors, this meal is sure to leave you satisfied. The dish centers around savory-sweet bulgogi sauce, whisked with a bit of butter and spooned over succulent pork filet. There’s also tender roasted carrots and fluffy rice on the side. Yeah, this meal has a little bit of something for everyone.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/664cac0c5e4dc3c6a6a94117-ee35ade9.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67d9b78718d6e477003fcc3c-en-US.pdf
